<% content_for :title, "Research - Memora Medical Devices" %>
<% content_for :description, "Learn about our groundbreaking research into AI companion technology for seniors with dementia and cognitive decline." %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Memora Medical Research</h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Developing <span class="text-indigo-600">AI-Powered Companion Devices</span> for Dementia Care
      </h2>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We are researching and developing intelligent companion devices in the form of familiar stuffed animals, embedded with AI technology that enables natural conversation and interaction for seniors with dementia, paired with comprehensive caregiver insights.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Research Areas -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI Companion Design</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Researching the integration of conversational AI into familiar animal forms, creating natural interaction experiences that provide comfort and companionship through touch and voice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Caregiver Dashboard</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Developing secure online platforms that provide families and caregivers with meaningful insights, interaction summaries, and behavioral metrics while maintaining patient privacy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Interaction Analytics</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Analyzing conversation patterns, engagement levels, and emotional responses to optimize the AI companion's ability to provide appropriate responses and therapeutic interactions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Current Research Focus -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Current Research Focus</h3>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Companion Animal Technology</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We are developing soft, tactile companion animals embedded with advanced AI systems that can engage in natural conversations, respond to touch, and provide emotional comfort through familiar animal interactions.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>• Voice recognition and natural conversation</li>
            <li>• Touch-sensitive response systems</li>
            <li>• Familiar animal forms (cats, dogs, birds)</li>
            <li>• Personalized interaction patterns</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Caregiver Insight Platform</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We are creating secure online dashboards that provide families and professional caregivers with valuable insights into their loved one's daily interactions, mood patterns, and engagement levels.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>• Daily interaction summaries and recordings</li>
            <li>• Mood and engagement tracking</li>
            <li>• Behavioral pattern analysis</li>
            <li>• Communication trends and alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Research Methodology -->
    <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Research Methodology</h3>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 text-center">
          We employ rigorous scientific methodologies to ensure our AI companion technology is safe, effective, and beneficial for seniors with dementia and their care teams.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Clinical Trial Design</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Multi-phase studies following FDA guidelines for medical device development, with randomized controlled trials to measure efficacy and safety outcomes.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• Phase I: Safety and feasibility studies</li>
              <li>• Phase II: Efficacy evaluation</li>
              <li>• Phase III: Large-scale validation</li>
              <li>• Long-term follow-up protocols</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Data Collection & Ethics</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Comprehensive data collection with strict privacy protections, IRB approval, and ethical oversight to ensure participant safety and data security.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• HIPAA-compliant data handling</li>
              <li>• Informed consent protocols</li>
              <li>• Third-party safety monitoring</li>
              <li>• Regular ethical review processes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Research Goals -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Research Objectives</h3>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Our research program is designed to establish the scientific foundation for AI-powered dementia care solutions through evidence-based development and validation.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Primary Objectives</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• Validate AI companion animal safety and acceptance</li>
              <li>• Optimize natural conversation algorithms</li>
              <li>• Measure engagement and comfort levels</li>
              <li>• Develop meaningful caregiver insights</li>
              <li>• Test tactile interaction effectiveness</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-4">Research Questions</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• Do AI companion animals reduce isolation and anxiety?</li>
              <li>• How do tactile interactions enhance AI engagement?</li>
              <li>• What conversation patterns are most therapeutic?</li>
              <li>• How can caregivers best utilize interaction data?</li>
              <li>• Which animal forms provide optimal comfort?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
          <p class="text-indigo-800 font-medium text-center">
            "We're combining the therapeutic power of animal companionship with advanced AI to create meaningful connections for those living with dementia, while providing their loved ones with valuable insights into their daily experiences."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
